oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Aykroyd, Elizabeth, 1869 May 03
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of Elizabeth Aykroyd, dated December 12th, 1868. Illustrates the first page of the document. Aykroyd’s will was presented for probate to the Davidson County Court on May 3rd, 1869. Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
